tafsir[11]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe Allah …ďe sakkii yim…ďe …ďen e diina Makko kan, Allah bonnii fii golle ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  47,2,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe Allah, …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, …ďe gom…óini ko Allah jippini kon e Nulaa…óo Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) - on goonga immor…óo e Joomi ma…ď…ďe - O yawtanii …ďe bon…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, O mo∆ī∆īinii kadi fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe on aduna e laakara."
  47,3,"Ko wa…ói si …óin feddeeji …ói…ói yo…ďitiraa non, ko ko tawi kon yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen jokkii meere nden, gom…óim…ďe Allah e Nulaa…óo mun on kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Jommi ma…ď…ďe. Fedde kala yo…ďiraa ko haandi kon. Awa ko wano Allah …ďannginiri non √Īaawoore …óin feddeeji …ói…ói : gom…óim…ďe e heefer…ďe, woni ko O piyiranta yim…ďe …ďen, mise ma…ď…ďe …óen. O humindira huunde kala e nanndo mun."
  47,4,"Onon muumini'en, si on hawrii e yeddu…ďe …ďen ka hare, ko soppugol daa…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, jokkiron non haa …óu…ó…óinon warugol …ďe. Si …óum wa…óii, ko ha…ď…ďugol koy…óe dahaa…ďe …ďen. Ko onon anndi si on accitiray …ďe nii tun, maa si …ďe yo…ďay soktiigu ngun. Fow e mun, jokkee ha…ďugol …ďe ngol, haa hare nden …ďuu…ďira silmugol …ďe ngol maa haldigal mon e ma…ď…ďe. Ko jantaa koo, ko …óum woni √Īaawoore Allah nden, si Allah muuyuno non, O wallirayno gom…óim…ďe …ďen e dow heefer…ďe …ďen, ko aldaa e hare, ko woni tun, O sar'inir jihaadi, fii jarribagol yoga mon e dow yoga: O ndaarndoo ha…ďoo…ďe …ďen ka muumini'en e …ďe ha…ďataa …ďen, O ndaarndora gom…óin…óo on kadi keefeero on; si gom…óin…óo on waraama, o naata Aljanna, si ko kanko keefeero on, on naata Yiite. Kala non waraa…ďe fii Allah …ďen, pellet, Allah yeebataa golle ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  47,5,"Arma O fewna …ďe goonga, e nguurndam ma…ď…ďe aduna, O mo∆ī∆īina fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe on."
  47,6,"√Ďalnde Darngal, O naadoyay …ďe Aljanna, mo O …ďannginannoo …ďe fii mun."
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe Allah,gollir…ďe ko O sar'ini,si on wallirii Allah, wallugol diina e Annabaajo Makko on ha…ďa heefer…ďe …ďen,O wallitoray on foolugol …ďe,O tabintina teppe mon …óen ka ha…ďidugol e ma…ď…ďe."
  47,8,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, hayrere e halakuyee woodanii …ďe, Allah bonnii kadi fii golle ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  47,9,"Ko wa…ói si on halakuyee yani e ma…ď…ďe, ko tawde …ďe a√Īii Alqur'aana nde Allah jippini nden e Nulaa…óo Makko on, fii hinde nodda e bajjin…óingol Mo. Allah bonni fii golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe wonti hayru…ďe aduna e laakara."
  47,10,"E …ďee fennoo…ďe yiilaaki e leydi ndin, …ďe teskoo ko honno battane …ďeya fennunoo…ďe ado ma…ď…ďe wa'unoo? ∆äum wonuno ko kaani. Tawde Allah muncituno cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin e hoore ma…ď…ďe, …ďe halkodii e …ďi…ó…ďe e jawle ma…ď…ďe. Awae hino woodani yeddu…ďe kala jamaanu e nokku."
  47,11,"Ko wa…ói sabu ndin njo…ďdi haalaandi e …óin feddeeji …ói…ói, ko tawde ko Allah woni walloowo gom…óim…ďe …ďen; hara non yeddu…ďe …ďen, ballo woo alanaa …ďe."
